data.description: Great quite neighborhood! Alberthill Ranch!  Great time to buy this home! This 4-bedroom 3 full bath a bonus room and large loft includes a FULLY PAID OFF SOLAR system for you to enjoy month to month either NO electricity bill to a much lower one.   As you walk in the 1st bedroom downstairs immediate to the entrance, very private with full bath and linen closet, great for guests, get away office or maybe that teen who needs some space, as you walk in you’ll see the large dining room, spacious cook’s kitchen with plenty of cabinetry, a very spacious walk in pantry and beautiful granite counter tops throughout, including a huge island that can sit 5 or 6 people with open concept to the living room with gas fire place for those cozy evenings, large windows light up the place, your media room/game room it's right next door, as you walk upstairs you’ll see a another very spacious area with plenty of possibilities, 2 good size bedrooms that share dual sinks bathroom. The master bedroom has great mountain views and includes and even larger bathroom also with dual sinks, soaking tub, a separate walk-in shower and huge walk-in closet. There are several ceiling fans throughout the house. Step into your large back yard with a gas fireplace for fun smore nights or for a cozy read outside, plenty of fruit trees, very nice stamped concreate and large dog run. Your community amenities include an Olympic size community pool with splash pad for the kids to have a blast, BBQ areas with view of the lake, well-kept parks and awesome views of the mountains all around the community, brand new elementary school located in the neighborhood and plenty of parks and play space nearby.
